    "Positional embedding: A learnable embedding P ∈ R T ×d added to the conv-net output. 3.",
    "Transformer encoder: L = 3 layers of multi-head self-attention (H = 8 heads) and two-layer MLP blocks, each with residual connections, dropout, and layer-normalization.",
    "The Transformer's decoder portion is excluded, since its typical role in generating sequential outputs (e.g.",
    "next-word prediction in NLP or time-series forecasting) is unsuitable for fixed-length classification tasks.",
    "Omitting the decoder roughly halves the total number of parameters, significantly reducing computational cost without sacrificing classification performance. 4."
